site_title: Among Us Character Bookmark by Wilson Lee

block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Among Us there is an Imposter!!! I was inspired to make this Among Us Character bookmark and within a few hours, here it is. This is the Among Us Character Bookmark by Me, Wilson Lee. No scissors, no glue, pure origami bookmark. This video is create to allow you to fold along me while learning how to fold this model. Try it out, I hope you like it. Enjoy!!! This is fold along version of my Quickie origami video here : https://youtu.be/T_8rXFCqC-0 Here at Heap Art, we are trying to help you practice origami on a regular bases. Every week I will select a minimum of 2 origami models and show you how to fold it. If you like origami and paper airplanes -- Please use the following link to subscribe to my channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/heapart?sub_confirmation=1 My Upload Schedule: Tuesday : A new Paper Airplane, part of my 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge Friday : A new Origami Model never seen before on my channel
